  <bioghist id="aspace_61b48f80be623a35da2b1cca3baeec3e">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The festival, a traditional part of Black History Month events at Cornell, is a Cornell student-led organization founded in 1976 by the late Rev. W. Jack Lewis, director of the Cornell United Religious Work.</p>  </bioghist>
